WEBVTT

00:11:59.723 --> 00:12:00.975
in and of itself.

00:12:02.627 --> 00:12:04.539
In that same oral history,

00:12:04.563 --> 00:12:07.072
Bonica claimed that pain

00:12:07.096 --> 00:12:11.353
is the most complex human experience.

00:12:12.215 --> 00:12:16.029
That it involves your past life,
your current life,

00:12:16.053 --> 00:12:18.243
your interactions, your family.

00:12:19.256 --> 00:12:21.811
That was definitely true for Bonica.

00:12:22.593 --> 00:12:25.264
But it was also true for my mom.

00:12:28.043 --> 00:12:31.342
It's easy for doctors to see my mom